codex
There are two workable foil-only patterns. The narrower one is not to touch `_distributePayout` at all for the frozen foil case: add a foil ETH resolver that computes the same spin outcome, but when `prizePoolFrozen` is true, emits the spin and recirculates the whole payout as lootbox value without calling `_distributePayout`.
